15#define GLOBE_RADIUS 6371.0e3

20struct Node
21{
22
23 double x, y, theta;
24
25 Node() {}
26
27 Node(double _x, double _y, double _theta)
28 : x(_x), y(_y), theta(_theta)
29 {
30 }
31
32 // Is skewed!
33 Node(double _lat, double _long, double base_latitude, double base_longitude, double _theta)
34 {
35 x = GLOBE_RADIUS * (_long - base_longitude) * std::cos(0.);
36 y = GLOBE_RADIUS * (_lat - base_latitude);
37 theta = _theta;
38 }
39};

45struct Lane
46{
47 int id, type;
48 std::vector<Node> nodes;
50 // Variables after spline fitting
51 bool spline_fit;
52 double length;
53 tk::spline spline_x, spline_y;
63 Lane(const std::vector<Node> &_nodes, double offset, int _type, int &_id)
64 : type(_type)
65 {
66 spline_fit = false;
67 id = _id;
68 _id++;
69
70 // Offset the nodes
71 nodes.reserve(_nodes.size());
72 for (auto &node : _nodes)
73 {
74 // Create a node at the offset from the center node
75 nodes.emplace_back(
76 node.x + offset * std::cos(node.theta - M_PI_2),
77 node.y + offset * std::sin(node.theta - M_PI_2),
78 node.theta);
79 }
80 }
81
85 void AssignSpline(const tk::spline &_spline_x, const tk::spline &_spline_y)
86 {
87 spline_x = _spline_x;
88 spline_y = _spline_y;
89 spline_fit = true;
90 }
91};

128 void AddLane(const std::string &_type, double width, bool two_way, int &id)
129 {
130 // The first lane we add needs to offset at the end, the rest at the start
131 if (plus_offset != 0.)
132 {
133 plus_offset += width / 2.;
134
135 if (two_way)
136 minus_offset -= width / 2.;
137 }
138
139 if (!_type.compare("road"))
140 {
141 if (two_way)
142 {
143 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_FREEWAY, id); // Main road is ON the reference
144 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, minus_offset - width, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_FREEWAY, id);
145
146 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset - width / 2., roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::ROADLINE_BROKENSINGLEWHITE, id);
147
148 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset + width / 2., roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::ROADEDGEBOUNDARY, id);
149 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, minus_offset - 3. / 2. * width, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::ROADEDGEBOUNDARY, id);
150 }
151 else
152 {
153 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_FREEWAY, id);
154
155 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, minus_offset - width / 2., roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::ROADEDGEBOUNDARY, id);
156 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset + width / 2., roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::ROADEDGEBOUNDARY, id);
157 }
158 }
159 else if (!_type.compare("crosswalk"))
160 {
161 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::CROSSWALK, id);
162 }
163 else if (!_type.compare("sidewalk")) // In some cases, we want a new way object, offset from the current one
164 {
165 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, plus_offset, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_SURFACESTREET, id);
166 if (two_way)
167 lanes.emplace_back(nodes, minus_offset, roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_SURFACESTREET, id);
168 }
169
170 // For the first added lane
171 if (plus_offset == 0.)
172 {
173 if (two_way)
174 {
175 plus_offset += width / 2.;
176 minus_offset -= 3. * width / 2.;
177 }
178 else
179 {
180 plus_offset += width / 2.;
181 minus_offset -= width / 2.;
182 }
183 }
184 }
185};

215 void ToMsg(roadmap_msgs::RoadPolylineArray &msg)
216 {
217 msg.road_polylines.reserve(ways.size());
218
219 // Load the ways one by one
220 for (Way &way : ways)
221 {
222 for (Lane &lane : way.lanes)
223 {
224 roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline line_msg;
225 line_msg.type = lane.type;
226 line_msg.id = lane.id;
227
228 geometry_msgs::Point point;
229 for (Node &node : lane.nodes)
230 {
231 point.x = node.x;
232 point.y = node.y;
233 line_msg.coords.push_back(point);
234 }
235
236 msg.road_polylines.push_back(line_msg);
237 }
238 }
239
240 msg.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
241 msg.header.frame_id = "map";
242 }
243
249 void ToMsg(nav_msgs::Path &msg)
250 {
251 // Save the road as reference trajectory
252
253 // Load the ways one by one
254 for (Way &way : ways)
255 {
256 for (Lane &lane : way.lanes)
257 {
258 // Look for the reference trajectory
259 if (lane.type == roadmap_msgs::RoadPolyline::LANECENTER_FREEWAY)
260 {
261 msg.poses.reserve(lane.nodes.size());
262
263 // geometry_msgs::Pose pose_msg;
264 // line_msg.type = lane.type;
265 // line_msg.id = lane.id;
266
267 // geometry_msgs::Point point;
268 geometry_msgs::PoseStamped pose_msg;
269 pose_msg.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
270 pose_msg.header.frame_id = "map";
271
272 for (Node &node : lane.nodes)
273 {
274 pose_msg.pose.position.x = node.x;
275 pose_msg.pose.position.y = node.y;
276
277 pose_msg.pose.orientation = RosTools::angleToQuaternion(node.theta);
278
279 msg.poses.push_back(pose_msg);
280 }
281 msg.header.stamp = ros::Time::now();
282 msg.header.frame_id = "map";
283 return;
284 }
285 }
286 }
287 }
